elements.2211.03002_03a0c4c5628aecd9c19291b46ef07: A generalization of the DeepWalk algorithm is node2vec
elements.2211.03002_4ac25a84c124e675aa1e9a15f3e1a: , which uses biased random walks to learn features that encode more complex relations of nodes, such as functional relationships

elements.2211.03002_195be9d76f01e899b9a8660a514b9: In this work, we have used all the direct transactions between XRP wallets in a week to construct a weekly weighted directed network
elements.2211.03002_bd4b76681b22465c92bb71791c0b5: Using the deep walk method, we have embedded weekly snapshots of the network in vector space
elements.2211.03002_5b426b1efed43fae3183297ba00b5: Deep walk encodes community information into nodal vectors using truncated random walks on the network
elements.2211.03002_c75513889dea953fcb0f24f0121ca: Once can explore other methods of embedding, such as node2vec, to study other regularities of the network
elements.2211.03002_e1caef4f6dd9d5f7055f2f5b88d3b: From the weekly snapshots of the regular nodal vector components, we calculate the correlation tensor at different time periods
elements.2211.03002_49bf16b31dc1550e51a7da314b2ee: We have used a double SVD to remove redundant information from the correlation tensor
elements.2211.03002_7173567941147be0e65cc8d223fb1: The significance of our result is shown by comparing it with the results of a randomized counterpart
elements.2211.03002_23a9336f669d2caba9170bebc4afc: The evolution of the largest singular value
elements.2211.03002_12365cdba9bba9addcfdb2dc7ebb9: shows distinctive behavior and it correlates significantly with the XRP/USD price
elements.2211.03002_c5ef094ff98ce530f57c0bf85178b: The decomposition of the correlation tensor into signal and noise components shows that correlation in the signal component decreases significantly during the bubble period
elements.2211.03002_a72a4da59d7ea1929bd42464006ee: We explain this decrease in the correlation during the bubble period by the evolution of community structure that shows disruptive behavior during the bubble period
elements.2211.03002_4a556853da5bf2203998926ab9b5b: The disruptive behavior of community structure has also been observed in the foreign exchange market during economic downturns
elements.2211.03002_8aabaaf674fe463a2effac6f1dfb6: In summary, we have developed a method of correlation tensor spectra from XRP transactions

elements.2211.03002_b8c67fd8cf4bc0b2e0ae06354d719: This method is very general and can be used to analyze the transactions of other assets.
